Hide your email address while tracking and exposing the websites that send you spam, no expiration, completely free. 


There are plenty of sites out there that do similar things. I wrote an application called whyspam.me you can use it to create Disposable Email, that gets forwarded to your personal inbox without exposing your information.

Then we track and expose the websites who send you spam.


